data.description: Oak Hill Park Subdivision home with 2-bedroom, 1-bath. This house has many possibilities!!! Currently has nice Vinyl floors throughout the living, dining, kitchen for easy maintenance. IRON FENCE, fenced all 3 front perimeters of the house. This can be your first time home purchase and-or your investment opportunity! Invest in your future by owning this lovely home. Open concept layout has many possibilities. Bring your design project to become a reality! Large yard. Nice covered driveway patio. Central air & heat. No HOA. House needs some updating but is priced accordingly. Schedule your showing and send your best offer today!
